<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ910320-0071</DOCNO><DOCID>910320-0071.</DOCID><HL>   Business Brief -- Zonic Corp.:   Venture Is Formed to Make   Industrial Testing Products</HL><DATE>03/20/91</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION</SO><CO>   ZNIC</CO><IN>FACTORY EQUIPMENT (FAC)</IN><LP>   Zonic Corp. said it will form a joint venture withSynergistic Technology Inc. to make industrial testingequipment.   The equipment, called shaker control products, shakes upnew products so manufacturers can see how the products willstand up to real environmental conditions, such as vibrationsfrom driving or launching a missile.</LP><TEXT>   The shaker control products, to be marketed world-wide byZonic, will use Zonic's hardware and Synergistic Technology'ssoftware.   Zonic, based in Cincinnati, makes and markets data andcomputer graphic systems used in industrial machinerymonitoring and maintenance systems. Synergistic Technology, aclosely held company based in Santa Clara, Calif.,specializes in advanced vibration control technology.</TEXT></DOC>